Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.75,0:23:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.79,0:23:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好过分
